question: Change your Discord profile picture to an embarrassing photo of yourself for 24 hours.
Send a voice message to this Discord server singing your favorite song.
Post a screenshot of your most recent DMs (with sensitive info blurred out) in this channel.
Go to a public Discord server and use only emoji to communicate for the next 10 messages.
Start a debate in a Discord channel about whether cereal is a soup.
Create a new Discord server with the theme "Things I'm Bad At" and invite 5 friends to it.
Send a friend request to the 10th person on your Discord friend list and start a conversation.
Change your Discord status to "I love [insert least favorite food]" for the next hour.
Join a random public Discord server and compliment the first person who sends a message.
Use Discord's Go Live feature to stream yourself doing a silly dance for 1 minute.
Send a flirty Discord message to the last person you DMed.
Take a mildly suggestive selfie and make it your Discord banner for an hour.
